claim.claim-text:
31. A method, comprising
receiving a first signal comprising a first dataset representative of an image of at least one of an end effector and a shaft of a tool assembly, wherein the end effector is configured to treat a target tissue;
generating a modified image of the at least one of the end effector and the shaft that includes a control panel, wherein the control panel comprises one or more control elements representative of one or more operating parameters of the robotic surgical system;
receiving an input to the control panel from a user, the input being effective to set a location of the control panel relative to a feature of the tool assembly.
